name: The Dispute
description: A dispute between the human agent and artificial creatures wearing generated kimonos - Curated assets used are generated using a runwayml GAN / model. The digital collage is handcrafted with Affinity and some simple Deep Dreaming got applied to certain areas in the process. This image outlines a momentum of the dispute of a human agent trying to apply cognitive and perceptive filters and the machine generated objects penetrating the human reality.
